# ====================================
# Notes
# ====================================

# REQUIRED vs OPTIONAL:
# - ANTHROPIC_API_KEY: Required for basic functionality
# - SUPABASE_*: Required for authentication and data persistence
# - Other AI providers: Optional, enable only the ones you want to use
#
# Multi-Model Support:
# - You only need API keys for providers you want to use
# - The app will default to Anthropic (Claude) if no model is selected
# - Each provider has different pricing and capabilities
# - Now supports 7 providers with 25+ models total
#
# Security:
# - Never commit .env.local to git (it's in .gitignore)
# - Keep your API keys secure and rotate them regularly
# - Use different keys for development and production
# - Monitor your API usage to prevent unexpected costs
#
# For more information:
# - See README.md for setup instructions
# - See MULTI_MODEL_IMPLEMENTATION_SUMMARY.md for model details
# - See TODO.md for implementation status
